      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Tom Mitchell</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~tom/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1c/TomMitchellWEF2017.jpg/300px-TomMitchellWEF2017.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/1/1c/TomMitchellWEF2017.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:TomMitchellWEF2017.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Tom Mitchell at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Economic_Forum\">WEF 2017</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Tom M. Mitchell</b>,<br />\nan American computer scientist and <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">AI</a> researcher with focus on <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">machine learning</a>. He is <a href=\"/Edward_Fredkin\" title=\"Edward Fredkin\">Edward Fredkin</a> University Professor and chair of the <i>Machine Learning Department</i> at <a href=\"/Carnegie_Mellon_University\" title=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, leading the development of the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Never-Ending_Language_Learning\">Never-Ending Language Learning</a> (NELLL) system. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1982_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1982 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_Mitchell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1982_...\">1982 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_Mitchell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1982 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Paul_E._Utgoff\" title=\"Paul E. Utgoff\">Paul E. Utgoff</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>1982</b>). <i>Acquisition of Appropriate Bias for Inductive Concept Learning</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-82\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI 1982</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.aaai.org/Papers/AAAI/1982/AAAI82-099.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ryszard_Michalski\" title=\"Ryszard Michalski\">Ryszard Michalski</a>, <a href=\"/Jaime_Carbonell\" title=\"Jaime Carbonell\">Jaime Carbonell</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>1983</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007%2F978-3-662-12405-5\">Machine Learning: An Artificial Intelligence Approach</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ryszard_Michalski\" title=\"Ryszard Michalski\">Ryszard Michalski</a>, <a href=\"/Jaime_Carbonell\" title=\"Jaime Carbonell\">Jaime Carbonell</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>1985, 2014</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.elsevier.com/books/machine-learning/michalski/978-0-08-051054-5?gclid=EAIaIQobChMItc_hsp_34AIVUeR3Ch2l9QcDEAYYASABEgKW4_D_BwEMachine\">Learning: An Artificial Intelligence Approach, Volume I</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Morgan_Kaufmann_Publishers\">Morgan Kaufmann</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ryszard_Michalski\" title=\"Ryszard Michalski\">Ryszard Michalski</a>, <a href=\"/Jaime_Carbonell\" title=\"Jaime Carbonell\">Jaime Carbonell</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>1986</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=21934\">Machine Learning: An Artificial Intelligence Approach, Volume II</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Morgan_Kaufmann_Publishers\">Morgan Kaufmann</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a>, <a href=\"/Jaime_Carbonell\" title=\"Jaime Carbonell\">Jaime Carbonell</a>, <a href=\"/Ryszard_Michalski\" title=\"Ryszard Michalski\">Ryszard Michalski</a> (<b>1986</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007%2F978-1-4613-2279-5\">Machine Learning: A Guide to Current Research</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wolters_Kluwer\">The Kluwer International Series in Engineering and Computer Science</a>, Vol. 12</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_Mitchell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Sebastian_Thrun\" title=\"Sebastian Thrun\">Sebastian Thrun</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>1993</b>). <i>Integrating Inductive Neural Network Learning and Explanation-Based Learning</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI1993\" title=\"Conferences\">IJCAI 1993</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://robots.stanford.edu/papers/thrun.EBNN_ijcai93.ps.gz\">zipped ps</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>1997</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/%7Etom/mlbook.html\">Machine Learning</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/McGraw-Hill\">McGraw Hill</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_Mitchell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i>The Discipline of Machine Learning</i>. CMU-ML-06-108, <a href=\"/Carnegie_Mellon_University\" title=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/%7Etom/pubs/MachineLearning.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i>Human and Machine Learning</i>. <a href=\"/Carnegie_Mellon_University\" title=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/%7Etom/pubs/HumanMachineLearning_11_2006_web.pdf\">slides as pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>Mining Our Reality, the emerging trend toward mining personal data</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Science_%28journal%29\">Science</a>, December 2009. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/%7Etom/pubs/Science2009_perspective.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_Mitchell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/c/Carlson:Andrew\">Andrew Carlson</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/b/Betteridge:Justin\">Justin Betteridge</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/k/Kisiel:Bryan\">Bryan Kisiel</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/s/Settles:Burr\">Burr Settles</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/h/Hruschka_Jr=:Estevam_R=\">Estevam R. Hruschka</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.aaai.org/ocs/index.php/AAAI/AAAI10/paper/view/1879\">Toward an Architecture for Never-Ending Language Learning</a></i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-2010\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI 2010</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.isca-speech.org/archive/interspeech_2011/i11_4002.html\">Neural Representations of Word Meanings</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/interspeech/interspeech2011.html\">INTERSPEECH 2011</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a>, et al. (<b>2015</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.aaai.org/ocs/index.php/AAAI/AAAI15/paper/view/10049\">Never-Ending Learning</a></i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-2015\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI 2015</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a>, et al. (<b>2018</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://cacm.acm.org/magazines/2018/5/227193-never-ending-learning/fulltext\">Never-Ending Learning</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 61, No. 5</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_Mitchell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~tom/\">Tom Mitchell's Home Page</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_M._Mitchell\">Tom M. Mitchell from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=50076\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - Tom Mitchell</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=MnfzuPYAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Tom Mitchell - Google Scholar Citations</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://videolectures.net/mlas06_mitchell_sla/\">Semisupervised Learning Approaches - videolectures.net</a></li>\n<li> Brains, Meaning and Corpus Statistics by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom Mitchell</a>, March 27, 2009, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/QbTf2nE3Lbw?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_Mitchell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~tom/\">Tom Mitchell's Home Page</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.ml.cmu.edu/news/news-archive/2017/june/mitchell-world-economic-forum.html\">Tom Mitchell Represents CMU at 2017 World Economic Forum - Machine Learning</a> - <a href=\"/Carnegie_Mellon_University\" title=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</a>, June 29, 2017</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ml.cmu.edu/\">Machine Learning Department - Carnegie Mellon University</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~tom/publications.html\">Selected Publications by Tom Mitchell</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#RefDB\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Reference Database</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/m/Mitchell:Tom_M=\">dblp: Tom M. Mitchell</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228142234\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 120/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 274/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4373-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228142234 and revision 